Her A dress worn by Vivien Leigh when she played Scarlett O'Hara in the 1939 film fetched $137,000 at auction on Saturday in Beverly Hills . 
  Heritage Auctions offered the gray jacket and skirt, plus more than 150 other items from the Academy Award-winning film at auction . 
  The dress was worn in several key scenes in the film and was worn by Leigh in several scenes . 
  It was one of the top selling items in the auction . 
 